Sentencas: In order to improve cost competitiveness and the further application of metal-supported cells, it is important to explore cathodes suitable for low-temperature sintering.
Titulo: Self-assembly and low-temperature sintered La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ @ Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathode with rich electrode/electrolyte interface and enhanced performance in harsh condition

Sentencas: However, decreasing cathode sintering temperature while maintaining robust interface of cathode/electrolyte and decent electrochemical performances is challenging for solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Self-assembly and low-temperature sintered La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ @ Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathode with rich electrode/electrolyte interface and enhanced performance in harsh condition

Sentencas: Herein, by combining the Pechini method with one-pot method, La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-delta @ Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-delta (LSC@GDC) composite cathodes are prepared and investigated, compared with mechanically mixed LSC-GDC cathodes.
Titulo: Self-assembly and low-temperature sintered La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ @ Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathode with rich electrode/electrolyte interface and enhanced performance in harsh condition

Sentencas: At the cathode sintering temperature of 800 degrees C, the LSC@GDC cathode single cells perform better performances, with deceased resistances, improved power density outputs and better feasibility to wide oxygen partial pressures from 0.21 atm down to 0.03 atm.
Titulo: Self-assembly and low-temperature sintered La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ @ Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathode with rich electrode/electrolyte interface and enhanced performance in harsh condition

Sentencas: The optimum composition of 70:30 wt% for LSC@GDC is proposed.
Titulo: Self-assembly and low-temperature sintered La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ @ Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathode with rich electrode/electrolyte interface and enhanced performance in harsh condition

Sentencas: The anode supported single cell with LSC@GDC30 cathode exhibits a maximum power density of 0.789 W/cm(2) and 0.545 W/cm(2) at 750 degrees C, under cathode oxygen partial pressure of 0.21 atm and 0.03 atm, respectively.
Titulo: Self-assembly and low-temperature sintered La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ @ Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathode with rich electrode/electrolyte interface and enhanced performance in harsh condition

Sentencas: Moreover, the low temperature sintered LSC@GDC50 cathode performs decent durability during repeatedly controlled thermal cycling over 10 times.
Titulo: Self-assembly and low-temperature sintered La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ @ Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-δ composite cathode with rich electrode/electrolyte interface and enhanced performance in harsh condition
